  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nOne replicated study in Australia\u00a0found that frogs only bred once sex ratios were manipulated, along with playing recorded mating calls and moving frogs into an indoor enclosure which allowed temporary flooding, and had various types of organic substrate."
